About Me

Unveiling the
Layers of My Story

Hello, I am Aniketh Kapurubandara, a graphic designer passionate about creating visual stories. My approach focuses on unveiling the layers of a brand or idea, crafting designs that not only capture attention but also communicate the essence of the message. Every project is a unique opportunity to create something visually impactful and emotionally resonant."
